<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>JS Bin</title>
</head>
<body>

<script id="jsbin-javascript">
var people = [{name: "name", age: 41}, {name: "name", age: 48}, {name: "name", age: 22}, {name: "name", age: 37}]
var peopleOverForty = people.filter(function(x){
  if(x.age > 40){
    return true;
  }
  else{
    return false;
  }
});
console.log(peopleOverForty);
</script>

</script></body>
</html>
